lead_paragraph: The CONCACAF confederation which runs football in North and Central America and the Caribbean has chosen Soccer United Marketing (SUM) to sell its sponsorship rights for five years, it said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: CONCACAF Sells Sponsorship Rights, Funds Unfrozen
